CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FA taxi driver has thanked one of his
OL,8,Fpassengers for saving his life after a
OL,9,Fchance encounter led to a discovery
OL,10,Fthat he had prostate cancer.
OL,12,FIn the summer of 2024, driver Brian
OL,13,FKelly picked up Prostate Cancer UK
OL,14,Fvolunteer Tam Hewitt for what would
OL,15,Fprove to be a fateful trip across
OL,16,FGlasgow.
OL,18,FMr Hewitt, now 76, spoke to him about
OL,19,Fthe risks of prostate cancer and the
OL,20,Fimportance of getting checked for it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FLater, Mr Kelly became concerned about
OL,8,Fhis own health and went to see a GP,
OL,9,Frecalling his passenger's advice to
OL,10,Fseek a PSA blood test which can detect
OL,11,Fprostate cancer.
OL,13,FHe asked his doctor to carry this out
OL,14,Fdespite not feeling any symptoms, but
OL,15,Ffeeling compelled by the conversation
OL,16,Fin the taxi.
OL,18,FThe PSA results led to further tests
OL,19,Fwhich ultimately revealed two sites of
OL,20,Fprostate cancer, one of which was
OL,21,Faggressive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FThe taxi driver, 66, would go on to
OL,8,Freceive brachytherapy treatment in
OL,9,FJune 2025, just after his youngest
OL,10,Fdaughter's graduation.
OL,12,FThe early intervention meant the
OL,13,Fcancer was dealt with at stage two,
OL,14,Fbefore it could progress further.
OL,16,FHe was back at work within a week and
OL,17,Fis still feeling fit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FMr Kelly, who is from East Ayrshire,
OL,8,Fcredits Mr Hewitt for his life-
OL,9,Fchanging decision to seek the test,
OL,10,Fbut it was not until another chance
OL,11,Fencounter in December 2025 that he got
OL,12,Fthe chance to properly thank him.
OL,14,FIn a complete coincidence, Mr Kelly's
OL,15,Fcab was called to the Prostate Cancer
OL,16,FUK volunteer's house, where the pair
OL,17,Fwere reunited.
OL,19,FSpeaking to the Press Association, Mr
OL,20,FKelly said: "I knew the address, I
OL,21,Fknew where Tam lived.
OL,26,@|D@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,F"Again, he had material that we wanted
OL,8,Fto take with him, we were putting it
OL,9,Finto the back of the car.
OL,11,F"Once we had done that, I then broke
OL,12,Fthe news to him.
OL,14,F"I just shook his hand and said 'by
OL,15,Fthe way, I just want to thank you for
OL,16,Fsaving my life'."
OL,18,FAs they spoke further, Mr Kelly
OL,19,Fdiscovered that Mr Hewitt had also
OL,20,Fundergone brachytherapy to treat
OL,21,Fprostate cancer some 20 years ago.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FHe said: "Anyone who gets into my car
OL,8,Fwho's over a certain age, I have the
OL,9,Fconversation with them.
OL,11,F"I just throw out, 'You're of a
OL,12,Fcertain age, have you had this PSA
OL,13,Fblood test?'"
OL,15,FMr Hewitt regularly gives talks to
OL,16,Fraise awareness about prostate cancer,
OL,17,Foften organising pop-up stalls in
OL,18,Fhospitals and other venues.
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FThe 76-year-old, who is from Glasgow,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Although it's not the first
OL,9,Ftime someone has thanked me for having
OL,10,Fthe conversation that has led them
OL,11,Fchoosing to get a PSA test and an
OL,12,Fearly diagnosis I was completely taken
OL,13,Faback when Brian asked to shake my
OL,14,Fhand.
OL,16,F"If his treatment and journey works as
OL,17,Fwell as mine he will be delighted.
OL,26,@pD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,F"I have been raising awareness for
OL,8,Fover 20 years and currently average
OL,9,Fover 50 awareness stands per year
OL,10,Fbefore the talks and presentations."
OL,12,FHe added: "Results like this make it
OL,13,Fall worthwhile and I'm sure all our
OL,14,Fvolunteers will feel exactly the same."
OL,16,FJoseph Woollcott, Prostate Cancer UK's
OL,17,Fhead of health policy, said: "Brian
OL,18,Fand Tam's story is wonderful, and it
OL,19,Fshows the power of men talking and
OL,20,Flooking out for each other.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@dO]tD@KOUvD@gO]yD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,F"I'm so grateful to all our incredibly
OL,8,Fdedicated volunteers like Tam, who
OL,9,Fhave lifesaving conversations all the
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"One in eight men will get prostate
OL,13,Fcancer, and your risk doubles if
OL,14,Fyou're Black, so most of us will know
OL,15,Fsomeone living with or after the
OL,16,Fdisease.
OL,18,F"It's curable if found early, but it's
OL,19,Falso a complex disease that leaves
OL,20,Fmany feeling confused about the right
OL,21,Fpath to take.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779768224
OL,3,CTaxi driver tells passenger 'you saved
OL,4,Cmy life' after advice led to cancer
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,F"Men need people like Tam in their
OL,8,Fcorner, and at Prostate Cancer UK we
OL,9,Fare here to help men at every step of
OL,10,Ftheir journey from diagnosis to
OL,11,Ftreatment and with what comes next."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@dO]
